<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.6.10">
<l>tēvaraiyu macuraraiyun ticaikaḷaiyuṅ kaṭalkaḷaiyum maṟṟumuṟṟum</l>
<l>yāvaraiyu moḻiyāmē yemperumā ṉuṇṭumiḻnta taṟintucoṉṉa</l>
<l>kāvaḷarum poḻilmaṅkaik kalikaṉṟi yolimālai kaṟṟuvallār</l>
<l>pūvaḷarun tirumakaḷā laruḷpeṟṟup poṉṉulakil polivartāmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master learning the garland of verse by Kalikaṉṟi of Maṅkai,</l>
<l rend="indent">with groves where gardens grow,</l>
<l>Who spoke knowing of our lord’s consuming and disgorging</l>
<l rend="indent">deities and demons,</l>
<l>The quarters, the seas, all else and everyone, without leaving [anything],</l>
<l>Gaining grace by the lady Tiru who blooms from a blossom,</l>
<l rend="indent">they will prosper in the golden land.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
